headline: CyberNinja- An interactive learning platform
description: CyberNinja is an interactive learning platform that combines artificial intelligence and gamified elements to educate users about cybersecurity.

headline: ROOM-NEST (Plan your home online)
description: RoomNest is a web-based platform built to simplify hostel room booking and financial tracking for students. It allows users to search, book, and manage rooms digitally while maintaining a transparent record of rent, payments, and shared expenses.

headline: DreamTeamInsight
description: Developed an interactive Power BI dashboard named DreamTeam Insight to analyze batsmen vs bowlers performance for Fantasy 11 decision-making Performed data cleaning and modeling in Power Query, created DAX measures for key performance indicators (strike rate, economy, consistency), and visualized insights through dynamic charts and filters to help users form the best possible fantasy team.
